357
00:24:11,116 --> 00:24:12,284
Syukurlah kau kaya.

358
00:24:12,368 --> 00:24:14,203
Syukurlah kau berpikir begitu.

359
00:24:14,286 --> 00:24:16,914
Jadi, kau bukan lagi atlet nasional?

360
00:24:18,457 --> 00:24:20,668
Aku tak bisa menjadi atlet lagi.

361
00:24:20,751 --> 00:24:24,088
Aku hanya Ki Seon-gyeom.

362
00:24:26,715 --> 00:24:29,843
Kau tak takut tak bisa berlari lagi?

363
00:24:29,927 --> 00:24:30,969
Aku harus menerimanya.

364
00:24:34,306 --> 00:24:35,974
Hampir lupa.

365
00:24:36,809 --> 00:24:39,186
Aku sudah janji.

366
00:24:39,269 --> 00:24:40,771
