869
01:01:00,949 --> 01:01:02,868
KI SEON-GYEOM
ATLET

870
01:01:02,951 --> 01:01:05,120
AYAH: KI JEONG-DO
IBU: YOOK JI-WOO

871
01:01:06,872 --> 01:01:09,416
